                                    | This is a community based music web app which will allow the user to listen to music based on the mood user currently in, and the songs will be categorized into emotion groups based on the community, and the community will rank the songs. We are intending to implement in here is that we are using ranking algorithm to change songs after categorizing the songs according to user’s flavors. And we are taking the suggestions from the user to add new songs to our database
